Birth in space
Earth in danger.
Global warming or collision with killer asteroid.
Caravans of spaceships with strawberry inhabitants on board are looking for a replacement planet.
To save humanity, is the important question of how we can reproduce in the heavylessness or on the replacement planet?
I do not think there are many options.
